{"tid":2511322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HK Express 賣飛機手推車 限量發售附獨立生產編號","createTime":"2021-04-30T22:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T22:22:38.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e87c5a4ab4edab4e195c1ed0cf4a3013a8ee66a1","tid":2511322,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T22:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHK Express 在 Facebook 公佈消息，指官網即將販售幾款限量版的機上手推車以及手挽櫃。特別的是當中每一架都刻有獨一無二嘅生產編號，如同記錄每一架車仔的飛行歷程。官方表示，大家可以將手推車及手挽櫃變成實用的儲物櫃、茶几又或者是鞋櫃，讓大家就算在家中亦有飛行的感覺。不過，官方暫時未公報產品售價及何時開賣，如有興奮，大家可密切留意【官網商店】的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT9ttVgvsuqmZKuD5T9BvtJesgQPGKw6bB1JDXgcCYsPg?filename=YqQ7wWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqQ7wWS.png&h=b99c239d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66b3c3789cac0fb4b2fe6b052e487ea3db90e47d","tid":2511322,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T22:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKExpress/photos/a.139871409544881/1598709333661074/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKExpress%2Fphotos%2Fa.139871409544881%2F1598709333661074%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9c0b01a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKExpress/photos/a.139871409544881/1598709333661074/</a>"}]}